name: Open Port Check Tool - Test Port Forwarding on Your Router
caption: yougetsignal.com
description: The port forwarding tester is a utility used to identify your external IP address and detect open ports on your connection. This tool is useful for finding out if your port forwarding is setup correctly or if your server applications are being blocked by a firewall.
